section.clearCachesText: The cache is immediately cleared synchronously for all used adapters.
section.clearAndWarmUpText: After the cache has been cleared, new cache entries are generated asynchronously.
section.indexesText: All indexes are updated asynchronously. The progress can be viewed in the Notification Center. This includes for example the product and category indexes or the SEO URLs.

clearCache.error: A unknown error occurred, while deleting cache.

clearCacheAndWarmup.started: All caches cleared. Warmup starts now.

modal.title: Clear Caches
modal.message: Are you sure you want to clear all caches?
